General.Name: Hoylu AB
General.Description: Hoylu AB (publ) provides visual collaboration solutions for distributed teams. It primarily offers Hoylu Adaptive Workspaces that enable real-time synchronization and asynchronous work in different time zones, as well as integration with other video conferencing solutions and team-based applications, such as Microsoft Teams. The company also provides custom software development and professional services. Hoylu AB (publ) was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Norrköping, Sweden.
